Package edu.harvard.seas.pl.abcdatalog.engine.bottomup.concurrent

Class BottomUpEvalManager

java.lang.Object
edu.harvard.seas.pl.abcdatalog.engine.bottomup.concurrent.BottomUpEvalManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
EvalManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExtensibleBottomUpEvalManager
public class BottomUpEvalManager extends Object implements EvalManager
An evaluation manager that implements a saturation algorithm similar to semi-naive evaluation. It supports explicit unification.
